Port Notes:

----- version 1.2.0-1 -----
Version bump.

----- version 1.1.6-2 -----
The hspell module now builds automatically.

----- version 1.1.6-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.
As hspell provides only a static library, linking the hspell module 
required manual intervention.


Cygwin port maintained by:
http://cygwinports.dotsrc.org/
